$ Formatting text with Perl modules

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/Text/Aligner[`Text::Aligner`] has a single function that *justifies* text.

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/Text/Aligner[`Text::Autoformat`]

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/Text/Format[`Text::Format`] for formatting in various ways.

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/Text/Reform[`Text::Reform`] has functions for manual wrapping and reformatting.

→ development/languages/Perl/modules/Data/Formatter/Text[`Data::Formatter::Text`] to format *Perl data structures*, allowing for the type of the data.
